snippet.title: Johnny Depp's SECURITY Guard MALCOLM CONNOLLY Witness Statement
snippet.description:
In this witness statement Johnny Depp's security guard Malcolm Connolly confirms that Amber Heard was the abuser in the relationship and says she lied about the Australia incident in which Johnny Depp had his finger severed.
